  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will examine the feasibility and acceptability of yoga for adolescents seen by a
      medical practitioner for their headaches. The study will also examine whether yoga decreases
      anxiety and improves quality of life. We hypothesize that yoga will be both acceptable and
      feasible with a pediatric population. We also hypothesize that yoga will decrease anxiety and
      improve quality of life.
    </textblock>
